  "title": "Robotics Engineer (Aerospace)",
  "description": "<p><strong>Job Description:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>In charge of designing, developing and modify guidance, navigation, and flight control systems and algorithms for company aircraft systems.</li>\n  <li>Responsible in analyzing flight data to verify flight performance and to help to troubleshoot issues that are found during the flights of company drone systems.</li>\n  <li>In charge of selecting, testing, evaluating and integrating new sensors or navigation systems onto the company drone systems</li>\n  <li>In charge of the generating documentation on the specifications, design, test procedures and test results of the GNC systems and algorithms that were developed.</li>\n  <li>Responsible in developing and modifying 6-DOF and hardware-in-the-loop in simulation environments.</li>\n  <li>In charge of supporting ground and flight test activities</li>\n  <li>Responsible in participating in design and code reviews.</li>\n  <li>Working with the cross function departments </li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Job Requirement:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Minimum Degree in Mechanical/ Electrical/ Aerospace/ Mechatronics Engineering or relevant </li>\n  <li>Minimum 4 years of working experience in system modelling and control, analysis, and simulation in aircraft applications. and developing model-based design and analyses using MATLAB/Simulink.</li>\n  <li>Proficient in C/C++ programming language and software and development tools such as Linux, ROS and Git.</li>\n  <li>Knowledge in inertial and other type of sensors for navigation </li>\n  <li>Knowledge in Kalman filtering, digital signal processing and sensor data fusion.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>To submit your application, please apply online to <a href=\"mailto:apply@rn-care.com\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>apply@rn-care.com </strong></a>or call +(65) <a href=\"tel:6513 5697\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>6513 5697</strong></a> for private and confidential discussion.</p>\n<p>Your interest will be treated with the strictest of confidence. We regret that only shortlisted candidates will be notified or contacted.</p>\n<p><strong>RN Care Pte. Ltd</strong><br>\n<strong>EA License No: 17C8900</strong></p>",
